.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, lavender, mauve, brown, blood-red
There are 5 different nationalities: polish, mexican, brazilian, spanish, argentine
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, juice, fanta, almond-milk
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ebonymaster, fonseca, davidoff, old-henry, bolivar
5 different pets are kept: lizard, pony, mouse, rabbit, hamster
1. the polish is the person who likes mauve
2. the swedish is the owner of the mouse
3. the mexican is the person drinking fanta
4. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes brown
5. the person who likes lavender is the person drinking sprite
6. the davidoff-smoker is the owner of the pony
7. the person who likes blood-red is the fonseca-smoker
8. the person drinking juice is in the middle
9. the spanish is on the far left
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard
11. the owner of the hamsters is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker
12. the ebonymaster-smoker is the person drinking 7up
13. the brazilian is the old-henry-smoker
14. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony
15. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    blood-red	|     ebony	|      mauve	|     lavender	|     brown	|
| Nationality	|   spanish	|    mexican	|    polish	|    brazilian	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     lizard	|    hamster	|     pony	|     rabbit	|      mouse	|
| Beverage	|    almond-milk	|     fanta	|     juice	|    sprite	|      7up	|
| Cigar		|   fonseca	|    bolivar	|  davidoff	|    old-henry	|   ebonymaster	|
